8 . requests the secretary-general to seek the views of member states on the issue of the promotion of multilateralism in the area of disarmament and non-proliferation and to submit a report thereon to the general assembly at its sixty-third session ;
9 . decides to include in the provisional agenda of its sixty-third session the item entitled " promotion of multilateralism in the area of disarmament and non-proliferation " .
